{"Id":489,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-muhammadmakin","Author":"Muhammad Makin","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://quranenc.com/check/chinese_makin/v1.0.0-csv.1 , https://quranenc.com/en/browse/chinese_makin , https://quranenc.com ,","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"难道我没有用薄弱的精液创造你们吗？"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"我把它放在一个坚固的安息之所，"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"到一个定期。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":23,"Text":"我曾判定，我是善於判定的。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":24,"Text":"在那日，伤哉否认真理的人们。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":25,"Text":"难道我没有使大地成为包罗"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":26,"Text":"活物和死物的吗？"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":27,"Text":"我曾在大地上，安置许多崇高的山峦。我曾赏赐你们甘美的饮料。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":28,"Text":"在那日，伤哉否认真理的人们。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":29,"Text":"“你们去享受你们否认的刑罚吧！"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":30,"Text":"你们去享受有三个杈的荫影吧！”"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":31,"Text":"那荫影不是阴凉的，不能遮挡火焰的热浪。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":32,"Text":"那火焰喷射出宫殿般的火星，"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":33,"Text":"好像黧黑的骆驼一样。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":34,"Text":"在那日，伤哉否认真理的人们！"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":35,"Text":"这是他们不得发言之日。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":36,"Text":"他们不蒙许可，故不能道歉。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":37,"Text":"在那日，伤哉否认真理的人们！"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":38,"Text":"这是判决之日，我把你们和先民集合在一处。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":39,"Text":"如果你们有什么计谋，你们可对我用计。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":40,"Text":"在那日，伤哉否认真理的人们！"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":41,"Text":"敬畏的人们，必定在树荫之下，清泉之滨，"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":42,"Text":"享受他们爱吃的水果，"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":43,"Text":"将对他们说：“你们曾经行善，故你们痛快地饮食吧！”"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":44,"Text":"我必定要这样报酬行善者。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":45,"Text":"在那日，伤哉否认真理的人们。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":46,"Text":"你们暂时吃喝享受吧！你们确是犯罪的人。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":47,"Text":"在那日，伤哉否认真理的人们。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":48,"Text":"有人对他们说：你们当鞠躬。他们不肯鞠躬。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":49,"Text":"在那日，伤哉否认真理的人们。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":50,"Text":"除《古兰经》外，他们要信仰什么文辞呢？"}]}